      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6A37FB48-286A-4510-9AA2-14C9B586DFFD" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Sales Order line item is unconfirmed</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6E3F6371-4BA5-44DB-9701-E98F405EFAEF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1) From Change order - (assumptions) if there was a previous it commit will remain 
2) From Create order - no sales order generated</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-94B2242E-1648-4561-BD34-872268E891E0" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> 

1.Order type will be unconfirmed
 once saved
2.User has option to save or exit, 
if user exits sales order from
 creation then no sales order will
 be created. If user exits from 
change order then previous commit
 will remain, no changes applied</text>
      </textAnnotation>
